#: home/templates/articles/cl/article_0001.html:17
msgid ""
"A practical guide for expanding enterprises on incorporating in Chile, "
"obtaining a RUT, and running compliant payroll (UF, SII, AFP, FONASA/ISAPRE, "
"AFC, SIS, Legal Gratification) — with ExactusPay."
msgstr ""

#: home/templates/articles/cl/article_0001.html:46
msgid ""
"A step-by-step guide to incorporating in Chile and running compliant payroll "
"— including UF, statutory contributions, and Legal Gratification — powered "
"by ExactusPay."
msgstr ""

#: home/templates/articles/cl/article_0001.html:56
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Profile | ExactusPay"
msgid "Chile Payroll Guide | ExactusPay"
msgstr "Mwongozo wa payroll wa %(country_name)s | ExactusPay"

