#: home/templates/home/platform.html:1124
msgid "Bring global payroll under one roof"
msgstr "Leta mishahara ya kimataifa chini ya paa moja"

#: home/templates/home/platform.html:1126
msgid ""
"Get a single source of truth, standardised reporting, and compliance-ready "
